        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Infant Formula Made in America Act of 2024&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill allows a 30% investment tax credit for infant formula that is lawfully sold and manufactured in the United States. It also allows a domestic production tax credit for such infant formula.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
